<a name="contact"></a>
<section class="contact">
	<div class="container">
		<h1 style="margin: 0.4em 0;">Contact</h1>
		<p>Fill out your information below and let's talk about your project! You will get a response within 5 hours.</p>
		<form>
			<div class="form-group row">
				<div class="col-sm-6">
					<input type="text" style="height:46px;padding-top:10px" class="form-control floating-label input-lg" placeholder="Preferred Name">
				</div>
				<div class="col-sm-6">
					<input type="email" style="height:46px;padding-top:10px" class="form-control floating-label input-lg" name="optionRadio" placeholder="Email">
